07:40:27失去。 英国“天空”新闻网称，印度尼西亚交通运输部表示，已失联客机展开搜救调查。 英国广播公司称，机上有超过50人，目前情况不详。（来源：综合央视新闻、环球网）"}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlfHk6Pryx5hNEAMaCDU5NzQ3OTA2ILyS5v8FMBc4gAdABHIJNDM4NjEzMzQ2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=", "detail_text": "720 万热度", "trend": 0, "debut": false, "children": [{"type": "answer", "thumbnail": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-faa5aa20e4c68d10b7346b77e787313e_b.jpg"}]}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1610215074.960108", "card_id": "Q_438537142", "target": {"id": 438537142, "title": "如何看待推特永久停用特朗普个人账号？", "url": "https://api.zhihu.com/questions/438537142", "type": "question", "created": 1610150657, "answer_count": 2674, "follower_count": 7046, "author": {"type": "people", "user_type": "people", "id": "0", "url_token": "", "url": "", "name": "用户", "headline": "", "avatar_url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"}, "bound_topic_ids": [319, 22955, 159978, 175849, 586774], "comment_count": 170, "is_following": false, "excerpt": "当地时间1月8日晚，美国社交网站推特在声明称将永久停用美国总统特朗普的个人账号，停用理由是：“在审核特朗普账号近期推文及相关问题后，尤其是推文在平台及其他地方被解读的情况后，出于对后续煽动暴力风险的担心，我们已经永久停用了该账号。”"}, "attached_info": "ClYIlfHk6Pryx5hNEAMaCDU5NzMxMDA5IIHm4/8FMKoBOIY3QAVyCTQzODUzNzE0MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA8gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg==", "detail_text": "666 万热度", "trend": 0, "debut": false, "children": [{"type": "answer", "thumbnail": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6d3f1197cef78f7faa97f86616d43358_720w.png"}]}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1610215074.9606311", "card_id": "Q_438539939", "target": {"id": 438539939, "title": "大家教资面试都抽到了什么题？", "url": "https://api.zhihu.com/questions/438539939", "type": "question", "created": 1610153786, "answer_count": 156, "follower_count": 1277, "author": {"type": "people", "user_type": "people", "id": "0", "url_token": "", "url": "", "name": "用户", "headline": "", "avatar_url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"}, "bound_topic_ids": [622, 35835, 108339], "comment_count": 0, "is_following": false, "excerpt": ""}, "attached_info": "Cj8Il